General Optimizations

Make space entities:
1. Star entity, classname "star"
1a. must have mass and radius
1b. must have temperature and color that is generated from the temperature
2. Planet entity, classname "planet"
2a. If not a stray planet, must be parented to a star/planet
2b. If not a stray planet, must have parameters for an ellipse orbit around it's parent
2c. Must have mass and radius, if mass is below a certain threshold, it is a moon, and not a planet